column5: My daughter still dosen't wanna come out from my wife's tummy...
With this heat, do you blame her?
If that's where you think babies come out, you are in for a huge surprise.  All in good time.
Assuming its your first, you're in for an amzing experience!
don,t sweat it ... she'll come out when her cell phone minutes are up .
My son was just born on August 1.   He was 7 days late and my daughter was 10.  Both still had to be induced.  You may still have a while to wait.
thank you guys, I'll be more patient.   btw, my boy is 2 1/2 now. just can't wait to have a girl
Good luck.  Hope everything goes smoothly

My boy turns 3 on the 19th and our 2nd boy is coming in October.  Due dates are just a ballpark, they'll induce if it goes too long.  Hope it's a quick labour and best of luck with the nights over the next couple of months.
I still have to wait for New Years day to meet my new fishin buddy, Can't Wait !!
Watch out for those ultrasounds, sometimes they call a girl, and it comes out a boy. Happened to a few people I know... Caused a few last minute paint changes.
I heard sex sometimes gets labour going. with your expectant wife that is
